{
  "stem": "26792.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had been friends for about three years, very close friends.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were supposed to marry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He survived the war until the last day, I believe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he was made by the Latvians or Germans to dig mass graves to burn the dead corpses.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when the mass graves were dug, all the group was shot dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he did not survive the last days of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in the first place, you should know that Latvians are drunkards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There is no social gathering without a lot of vodka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, they're alcoholics and later on after the war, I found-- 1948, I found, in a ditch, very many empty bottles of vodka which were given to them probably by the Germans for shooting.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Almost each Latvian I know, almost, each Latvian is an alcoholic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the first place, they used to come together to eat, drink, and sing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "All their songs, even their national songs, not the anthem, but folk songs, had a parody against Jews, which throw the Jews into the river and let's kill them, something like that.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can imagine what I felt like, sitting among them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I had only one aim and didn't think of anything that-- of anything they're saying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Remember, remember forever their names, their surname, what schools they went to, what they were doing before the war, whatever you can.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have a mission.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why did the rest perish?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why did you stay alive?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And your mission is the oath you have given at the mass graves in [NON-ENGLISH], that if you stay alive, you will destroy as many of them as you can.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this is what I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were no sexual subjects.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
